{{item:3117}} and {{item:2045}} and {{item:3060}} or {{item:3222}}
...for a core Mage-Support build. If you want AP beyond that, simply build AP. Most if not all of your Utility scales with it. I usually get Morello's for the CDR and the Passive, Zhonya's for it's Active, and Void if I want my damage to stick.

I find myself going Banner more than Mikael's at the moment just because of how the meta is at the moment. The Aegis Aura is great in mid-game teamfights, and the Active can be used to create map pressure.


{{item:3504}} + Zeke's Herald was great if you had a protect the ADC comp... Then Riot removed Zeke's.
